{"tid":1090321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考試不合格 爸爸迫兒子當街打爛PS4","createTime":"2019-04-03T11:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T23:52:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6b787ad0c159af88a79b055e340dfc266b54a1","tid":1090321,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KZnzRhtfSAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKZnzRhtfSAY&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5ARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=a5126b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KZnzRhtfSAY</a><br />\n<br />\n外國一名父親不滿兒子考試不合格，迫他毀掉最心愛的家用遊戲機PlayStation 4，更將過程拍片放上網，片段引起熱議，有網民認為這位父親不應該找物件來出氣，擔心這樣做反會影響兒子的價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n科斯比（Tre Cosby）不滿幼子崔西（Tracy）成績欠佳，決定要教訓他。他先用垃圾膠袋袋起遊戲機帶下樓，再向兒子訓話，訓斥對方當天早上又再開PS4玩遊戲，他大罵：「對着鏡頭說，說說你為何不聽教。」<br />\n<br />\n科斯比本來要求崔西在屋內自行摧毀PS4，不過太太着他出門處理。崔西出門後已忍不住抽泣，科斯比說：「我不要再聽到。」再向對方遞上鐵筆並稱：「破壞它。你最好打下去&hellip;&hellip;大大力地打。」<br />\n<br />\n崔西哭着揮動鐵筆敲打PS4，不過科斯比不滿意，找來大石砸向PS4，然後將大石交給崔西要他照做一次。不過兒子好像不夠力，科斯比自己再用石砸向遊戲機。<br />\n<br />\n科斯比再命令崔西撿起鐵筆繼續破壞PS4，後來就說：「你就只做到這程度？來吧，你可以做得更好。」他將PS4放在車輪後開車輾過，然後再撿起遊戲機再擲在地上。<br />\n<br />\n網民看罷片段後，都批評科斯比這個教訓兒子的方式有問題，「教你的兒子在憤怒時破壞值錢的東西有甚麼好處？那男孩長大後將有問題」、「當他長大後就會破壞電視等等&hellip;&hellip;當他生氣的時候，將PS4沒收並告訴兒子要改善才會發還，就是這麼簡單」。有人就認為孩子成績退步可能有其他因素，應該主動去協助而不是發洩。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190403/59443644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59443644&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5ARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b6f5031b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59443644&h=1f9d5526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190403/59443644</a>"},{"pid":"497f9c15300dcd0c19bec7ad70ef41a14eaa786d","tid":1090321,"uid":38904,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"力架汁素咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb01ed7327199e79dbb2471b2f6cee39f8ed5e2","tid":1090321,"uid":63113,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"遲下佢個仔攞支鎗行住佢就知錯"},{"pid":"b4157e70dbfc3c7a8a4ee94da2ac4520877ddc68","tid":1090321,"uid":68395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"有錢"},{"pid":"fbe416db94ea15267eb9ddc75867713a91bd44cd","tid":1090321,"uid":235152,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"日本都有大驚少怪,個仔一買完返去開左一陣<br />\n就比老豆拉出去當場打爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99b819967ad0c33835c4d8b300139871cc8c214","tid":1090321,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"部嘢咪又係老豆嘅property <br />\n<br />\n點樣整都冇問題啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1ac0a67794e953fce0054e826d1f1e2c292f8c","tid":1090321,"uid":18948,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"細個畀呀媽收 PS 條三色線同火牛，過幾日自己買咗一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f11df522159c1a3509b6b70358a4ac996f757e","tid":1090321,"uid":45854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"包到實又冇殘骸個樣<br />\n好假"},{"pid":"093b633d39f45cbe13e2f6e7b40ce5ce92912e87","tid":1090321,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"睇間屋都feel 到唔自在呢d 野<br />\n就好似好有錢既KOL 成日拎d 新野黎拆<br />\n佢都係wfc<img src=\"/assets/fac